OL,3,CFormer GP admits further murder plot
OL,4,Cusing fake wine
OL,6,FA former GP jailed for trying to
OL,7,Fmurder his mother's partner by
OL,8,Finjecting him with a fake Covid jab
OL,9,Fhas admitted to an earlier attempt to
OL,10,Fmurder him using wine laced with
OL,11,Fpoison.
OL,13,FThomas Kwan, 54, of no fixed abode,
OL,14,Fsent bottles of wine from a fake wine
OL,15,Fclub, laced with thallium - a chemical
OL,16,Fpreviously used in rat poison - to his
OL,17,Fmother's then-partner Patrick O'Hara.
