OL,3,CFormer GP admits further murder plot
OL,4,Cusing fake wine
OL,6,FNewcastle Crown Court heard how Kwan
OL,7,Fhad sent 18-21 bottles of wine to
OL,8,FO'Hara from the fictitious Northern
OL,9,FWine and Drinks Tasting Gentlemen's
OL,10,FClub between September 2022 and
OL,11,FJanuary 2024. Some of the bottles were
OL,12,Fpoisoned.
OL,14,FPeter Makepeace KC, prosecuting, said
OL,15,Ftwo bottles recovered contained poison
OL,16,Fand there was evidence that a third,
OL,17,Fwhich was laced with thallium, caused
OL,18,FMr O'Hara to fall ill.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
