OL,3,CFormer GP admits further murder plot
OL,4,Cusing fake wine
OL,6,FMr Makepeace said not all of the
OL,7,Fbottles were found to contain poison
OL,8,Fas Mr O'Hara would have swiftly fallen
OL,9,Fill, "quickly bringing the scheme to a
OL,10,Fhalt".
OL,12,FHe added: "Genuine bottles were sent
OL,13,Fto lure the victim into a sense of
OL,14,Fsecurity."
OL,16,FKwan was also charged with
OL,17,Fadministering noxious substance,
OL,18,Frelating to O'Hara's son in law
OL,19,FTorquil Gundlach who who was gifted a
OL,20,Fbottle of the wine.
