OL,3,CFormer GP admits further murder plot
OL,4,Cusing fake wine
OL,6,FKwan appeared at the hearing at
OL,7,FNewcastle Crown Court via videolink
OL,8,Ffrom HMP Frankland. He pleaded guilty
OL,9,Fto both charges and is due to be
OL,10,Fsentenced on 30 January 2026.
OL,12,FKwan had already been sentenced to a
OL,13,Flife sentence with a minimum term of
OL,14,F31 years in prison for a separate
OL,15,Fcount of attempted murder, also
OL,16,Fagainst Patrick O'Hara, after
OL,17,Finjecting him with a fake Covid jab
OL,18,Fwhile wearing a disguise.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
