OL,3,CFormer GP admits further murder plot
OL,4,Cusing fake wine
OL,6,FDuring that earlier trial, Newcastle
OL,7,FCrown Court heard how Kwan had sent
OL,8,Ffake NHS-headed letters to Patrick
OL,9,FO'Hara, before visiting him at his
OL,10,Fhome in Newcastle and administering an
OL,11,Finjection containing the chemical
OL,12,FIodomethane.
OL,14,FThe injection Mr O'Hara to suffer from
OL,15,FNecrotising Fasciitis, leading to him
OL,16,Fbeing placed in intensive care at the
OL,17,FRoyal Victoria Infirmary.
