OL,3,CFormer GP admits further murder plot
OL,4,Cusing fake wine
OL,6,FThe Court was told that Kwan was angry
OL,7,Fafter learning his mother had made a
OL,8,Fwill which allowed Mr O'Hara to stay
OL,9,Fin her home should she die before him.
OL,11,FKwan, who was living in Ingleby
OL,12,FBarwick at the time of the offences,
OL,13,Fhad been working as a GP at Happy
OL,14,FHouse surgery in Sunderland.
OL,16,FDuring investigations, officers
OL,17,Fdiscovered dangerous chemicals amassed
OL,18,Fby the GP, as well as instructions on
OL,19,Fhow to make the chemical weapon ricin
OL,20,Fon his computer.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
