OL,3,CFormer GP admits further murder plot
OL,4,Cusing fake wine
OL,6,FIn September 2025, a medical
OL,7,Fpractitioners tribunal determined that
OL,8,FKwan was no longer fit to practice
OL,9,Fmedicine and should be struck off.
OL,11,FTribunal chair Gerry Wareham said:
OL,12,F"The tribunal had no doubt that a
OL,13,Fsanction of erasure was the only
OL,14,Foutcome that would adequately mark the
OL,15,Fseriousness of the conviction, protect
OL,16,Fthe public, maintain public confidence
OL,17,Fin the profession and promote and
OL,18,Fmaintain proper standards of conduct
OL,19,Ffor members of the profession."
