OL,3,CFormer GP admits further murder plot
OL,4,Cusing fake wine
OL,6,FSpeaking to the tribunal via
OL,7,Fvideolink, Kwan said: "I just wanted
OL,8,Fto say that I sincerely apologise to
OL,9,FMr A, his family, my ex-colleagues, my
OL,10,Ffamily and everybody who's been
OL,11,Faffected by my actions."
OL,13,FHe said: "I accept the sanction being
OL,14,Fplaced upon me by the tribunal. I have
OL,15,Fnothing further to say."
